  </div>

  <footer class="bsk-footer bsk-footer-default">
    <div class="bsk-container-fluid">
      Footer content <a href="#" class="bsk-tb-colour-swatch-71B2D7">with link</a></div>
    </div>
  </footer>

  <h4 class="bsk-tb-margin-top bsk-tb-sample-sub-heading"><code>$bsk-colour-std-sky-blue-lighter</code></h4>

  <div class="bsk-row">
    <div class="bsk-col-12-md-4">
      <div href="#" class="bsk-thumbnail bsk-thumbnail-inverse">
