  <h4>Notes</h4>
  <ul>
    <li>This experiment was used to determine which variant of sky-blue should be used for links in inverse components</li>
    <li>It was used when the GDS colour scheme was integrated into the Style Kit and the standard colour scheme was developed</li>
  </ul>
